profile:
Inspector David Fairbairn is a Vancouver building expert, and has been featured on Global TV News and in the 24 Newspaper. He brings a passion for a "job well done" to every inspection and works hard for you - the customer!
 
SEVEN GREAT REASONS TO USE US:
 
1) Inspections Done Right – You get an unconditional money-back guarantee on your inspections.
 
2) No Waiting – You will receive your digital inspection report the same day as the inspection – guaranteed.
 
3) Peace of Mind – You get a fully Bonded, Licensed and Insured company.
 
4) Quality Inspection Reports - No “checklists” – You get a 220-point, full-color report with photographs, to ensure an easy-to-read, but thorough understanding of the issues and features of your home.
 
5) Uncover Problems before they Show – We use only the latest tools and technology – Moisture Reading and IR Thermal Imaging available (optional)
 
6) FREE Home Maintenance Book - “Now That You’ve Had a Home Inspection”, featuring tips, tricks and maintenance info on your new home. Included with every inspection.
 
7) Service for Life – You get personal support, 24/7 after the inspection.
 
CALL TODAY FOR A QUOTE! - 604 395-2795

Janzen Home Inspections serves Vancouver and the Lower Mainland, with licensed, certified, professional home inspectors dedicated to providing the most complete home inspections using the most up-to-date training and equipment. Janzen Home Inspections works with you from start to finish, with home inspections services that go above and beyond expectations.

Our Services
We will inspect your home as if it were our own.

Janzen Home Inspections offers the most comprehensive home inspections for buyers, sellers, and homeowners. Our home inspections go above and beyond the standards set by the province of British Columbia. We’ll inspect more than 500 components, examining each component for structural soundness, proper function, and code compliance. We’ll use our thermal imaging camera as needed to identify defects that may not be visible to the naked eye.

Using the latest tools, equipment and systems we inspect the following readily accessible area:

Foundation
Grading and drainage, including guttering
Roof covering materials
Roof structures and attics
Interior and exterior walls
Ceilings and floors
Doors and windows
Interior and exterior stairways
Fireplaces and chimneys
Porches, balconies, decks, and carports
Electrical systems
Heating, systems
Plumbing systems and fixtures
Major appliances
Garages and garage door openers
And much more…
